689
00:43:12,100 --> 00:43:13,226
Sim, senhor.

690
00:43:14,227 --> 00:43:15,228
Elijah.

691
00:43:15,812 --> 00:43:17,939
Melhoraste a nota no teste de ortografia?

692
00:43:18,022 --> 00:43:19,065
Sim, senhor.

693
00:43:19,148 --> 00:43:20,775
Vamos dar graças.

694
00:43:27,615 --> 00:43:29,033
Onde estás?

695
00:43:29,117 --> 00:43:31,536
